{
  "stem": "15694.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I saw a train there, a short train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I couldn't go very near.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In the middle of the train, I saw a bare-headed man, and the hairstyle and mustache was unmistakably Hitler.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was going to go a little nearer, but there were soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I didn't dare.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the train had already started rolling, and as it is in woods, I saw the picture here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now you see it, now you don't, now you see it, now you don't.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now I was standing now, and waiting, mesmerized, to hear and listen for the crash that might have changed or would change history.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "As I said it before, might have changed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because I'll never know what happened, but the train went on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was no crash.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now, whether some patrol found the obstacle or a local farmer saw it and removed it out of fear, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I was at first very disappointed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Only later, when I thought about this incident, and thinking what happened when, as in the beginning of my story, one German was shot in Paris, and they burned down all the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Under the pretext what I had done, the Holocaust would then be put-- the finger would have pointed at me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And those moments are only consolation, because it was autumn, 1940-42.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Although, perhaps, I would guess 2 million Jews have been killed at that time already, but the bulk was still to come.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The worst was still to come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I said, if his henchmen had continued with the Holocaust, they would have had this excuse, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, something to go back a little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just before my mother left, there was a conversation going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
